{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"a1297a2cb2","title":"晚王尔琢联","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"c4ad22428d","index":0,"year":1928,"month":10,"day":null,"articleId":"a1297a2cb2"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji4-1","name":"毛泽东全集第4卷(1)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji4-1.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji4-1":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"3603d7d081","type":"paragraph","text":"晚王尔琢联！","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"a1297a2cb2"},{"id":"e6a5e89a93","type":"paragraph","text":"（1928年10月）一哭尔琢，再哭尔琢，尔琢今已奖！留却重任谁承受生为阶级，死为阶级，阶级后如何？得到胜利方始休！","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"a1297a2cb2"},{"id":"602f19d324","type":"paragraph","text":"[1]王尔琢（1901—1928），字蕴玻，湖南省石门县商溪乡王官桥村人，黄埔军官学校第一期毕业。1924年加入中国共产党。1927年参加八一南昌起义，后又参加湘南暴动。1928年4月上井冈山和毛泽东会师，部队改编为工农红军第四军，任参谋长兼红军第二十八团团长。1928年8月25日，追赶叛徒时，在江西省崇义县思顺握被叛徒袁崇全枪杀。王尔球辆性后，朱德赶到思顺现场，痛哭和慎念战友。10月上句，在宁冈碧市举行追博会。追慎会前毛泽东在宁冈县茅坪村八角楼起草，由陈毅书写了这副换联，挂在会场两边。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"a1297a2cb2"},{"id":"a2b8262790","type":"paragraph","text":"为了改善根据地医疗条件，根据湘赣边特委决定于1928年10月，在井冈山西北的小井兴建一座红军医院。图为小井红军医院旧址。井冈山时期，毛泽东给伤员送饭用过的篮子。西江月·开冈山","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"a1297a2cb2"},{"id":"9a26e43aac","type":"paragraph","text":"（1928年秋）山下族旗在望，山头鼓角以相闻。敌军围因万千重，我自追然同不动。早已森严壁垒，更加众志成城。黄洋界M上炮声隆，","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"a1297a2cb2"},{"id":"83c9b49dbd","type":"paragraph","text":"报道敌军宵道。[1]井冈山，在江西西部及湖南东部，方圆500里，21鼓角，本指古代军中所用的战鼓和号角，此处借指军号。[3]消然，高峻独立。141黄洋界，并冈山五大哨口之一，另4个是八面山、双马石、朱砂","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"a1297a2cb2"},{"id":"9d5ce88785","type":"paragraph","text":"电！45w","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"a1297a2cb2"},{"id":"822b63aef3","type":"paragraph","text":"8","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"a1297a2cb2"},{"id":"09e984b664","type":"paragraph","text":"3..","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"a1297a2cb2"},{"id":"d68bc8e0f0","type":"paragraph","text":"AC我惠","index":9,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"a1297a2cb2"},{"id":"1974833fd0","type":"paragraph","text":"","index":10,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"a1297a2cb2"},{"id":"6e658da1dd","type":"paragraph","text":"1a...","index":11,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"a1297a2cb2"},{"id":"3b25f48bcf","type":"paragraph","text":"学a","index":12,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"a1297a2cb2"},{"id":"c709a27f35","type":"paragraph","text":"馆","index":13,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"a1297a2cb2"},{"id":"2694d6c35e","type":"paragraph","text":"8","index":14,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"a1297a2cb2"},{"id":"ea5f245eaa","type":"paragraph","text":"《革命圣地井冈山》（诗意画）","index":15,"publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"a1297a2cb2"}],"page":{"id":"8d08fc8e7b","publicationId":"maoquanji4-1","articleId":"a1297a2cb2","start":146,"end":150}}}},"__N_SSG":true}